OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F421A1774444274
OL,3,CRomance fraudster jailed after conning
OL,4,Cmen into funding her expensive
OL,5,Clifestyle
OL,7,FA model turned romance fraudster who
OL,8,Fconned men into spending tens of
OL,9,Fthousands of pounds to fund her
OL,10,Fexpensive lifestyle, has been jailed.
OL,12,FGemma Kingsley was described by a
OL,13,Fjudge at Swindon Crown Court as a
OL,14,F"common thief who traded on her charm,
OL,15,Fcharisma and good look" as he
OL,16,Fsentenced her to seven years and seven
OL,17,Fmonths in prison on Wednesday (25
OL,18,FMarch).
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/11
