CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F421A1774444274
OL,3,CRomance fraudster jailed after conning
OL,4,Cmen into funding her expensive
OL,5,Clifestyle
OL,7,FThe 50-year-old, of Beadnell,
OL,8,FNorthumberland, pleaded guilty to more
OL,9,Fthan a dozen counts of theft and fraud
OL,10,Fat the same court last month.
OL,12,FOver four years, police said Kingsley
OL,13,F"wove a web of lies" with several
OL,14,Fvictims, tricking men into
OL,15,Frelationships with her.
OL,17,FShe told them she was soon to inherit
OL,18,Fa large fortune from her grandfather,
OL,19,Fcompelling them to spend huge sums of
OL,20,Fmoney on her behalf, including on a
OL,21,Fplanned wedding.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
