PN,42103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F421A1774444274
OL,3,CRomance fraudster jailed after conning
OL,4,Cmen into funding her expensive
OL,5,Clifestyle
OL,7,FOn other occasions, she stole or used
OL,8,Ffalse bank card details to spend
OL,9,Fthousands of pounds on hotel stays.
OL,11,FWiltshire Police have released footage
OL,12,Fof the moment the force tracked down
OL,13,FGemma Kingsley in a remote cottage in
OL,14,FScotland
OL,16,FWiltshire Police previously said that
OL,17,Fin 2019, the force received a report
OL,18,Fthat Kingsley had fraudulently used
OL,19,Fthe bank details of her mother's
OL,20,Ffriend to pay for a stay at Cromhall
OL,21,FFarm, near Chippenham.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/11
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
