FL,422,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F421A1774444274
OL,3,CRomance fraudster jailed after conning
OL,4,Cmen into funding her expensive
OL,5,Clifestyle
OL,7,FAn investigation was launched, and
OL,8,Fseveral investigations into Kingsley
OL,9,Ffrom other forces were passed to the
OL,10,Fforce.
OL,12,FDetectives found that between January
OL,13,F2016 and January 2018, Kingsley was in
OL,14,Fa relationship with the victim, during
OL,15,Fwhich she informed him she was due to
OL,16,Freceive a multi-million-pound
OL,17,Finheritance, producing forged letters
OL,18,Ffrom professionals as proof.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/11
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
