PN,42105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F421A1774444274
OL,3,CRomance fraudster jailed after conning
OL,4,Cmen into funding her expensive
OL,5,Clifestyle
OL,7,FCourt documents show Kingsley told the
OL,8,Fvictim she was inheriting a "total
OL,9,Finheritance fund" of #42 million from
OL,10,Fher grandfather and added that a
OL,11,Fsolicitor had said she would be
OL,12,Freceiving #16 million.
OL,14,FAs a result, the victim spent tens of
OL,15,Fthousands of pounds on furniture for a
OL,16,Fnew home, dental bills, her debts and
OL,17,Fa payment for a wedding which did not
OL,18,Ftake place on the assumption he would
OL,19,Fsoon be reimbursed through the
OL,20,Finheritance.
OL,26,@pD@]OUqD@QO]
