OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F421A1774444274
OL,3,CRomance fraudster jailed after conning
OL,4,Cmen into funding her expensive
OL,5,Clifestyle
OL,7,FShe also repeatedly used his bank
OL,8,Fcards to steal money and opened a
OL,9,Fbetting account in his name, into
OL,10,Fwhich she put a large amount of his
OL,11,Fmoney, which she then lost through
OL,12,Fgambling.
OL,14,FThis victim "lost in excess of
OL,15,F#100,000" after falling for her lies,
OL,16,Fthe documents show.
OL,26,@vD@MOUwD@IO]
