OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F421A1774444274
OL,3,CRomance fraudster jailed after conning
OL,4,Cmen into funding her expensive
OL,5,Clifestyle
OL,7,FFollowing the breakdown of this
OL,8,Frelationship in 2018, the following
OL,9,Fyear Kingsley started a relationship
OL,10,Fwith another victim, again misleading
OL,11,Fhim into believing she was about to
OL,12,Finherit a large fortune.
OL,14,FAs a result, he assisted her with
OL,15,Fsignificant deposits for a Land Rover
OL,16,Fand a Porsche, as well as expensive
OL,17,Fhotel stays for which they had no
OL,18,Fmeans to pay.
OL,20,FThe victim also incurred a large debt
OL,21,Fthrough her use of his bank cards.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G7/11
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
