OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F421A1774444274
OL,3,CRomance fraudster jailed after conning
OL,4,Cmen into funding her expensive
OL,5,Clifestyle
OL,7,FIn two further brief relationships in
OL,8,Fthe autumn of 2019, Kingsley again
OL,9,Frepeatedly used the victims' personal
OL,10,Fand company bank cards to make
OL,11,Fpurchases without their knowledge.
