OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F421A1774444274
OL,3,CRomance fraudster jailed after conning
OL,4,Cmen into funding her expensive
OL,5,Clifestyle
OL,7,FPolice also found that Kingsley had
OL,8,Fcommitted theft and fraud against
OL,9,Fnumerous other victims, including
OL,10,Fsolicitors' firms, lawyers and a bank,
OL,11,Fby falsifying documents and letters.
OL,13,FKingsley was later charged with
OL,14,Fvarious offences but failed to attend
OL,15,Fcourt.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G9/11
