OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F421A1774444274
OL,3,CRomance fraudster jailed after conning
OL,4,Cmen into funding her expensive
OL,5,Clifestyle
OL,7,FAt a previous hearing she pleaded
OL,8,Fguilty to six counts of theft, four
OL,9,Fcounts of fraud by false
OL,10,Frepresentation, two counts of using a
OL,11,Ffalse instrument with intent that it
OL,12,Fwill be accepted as genuine, and one
OL,13,Fcount of being in possession of an
OL,14,Farticle for use in fraud.
OL,16,FJailing Kingsley, Judge Jason Taylor
OL,17,FKC told her: "Your duplicity and brass
OL,18,Fneck is staggering.
OL,26,@yD@NOU
