OL,3,CRomance fraudster jailed after conning
OL,4,Cmen into funding her expensive
OL,5,Clifestyle
OL,7,F"You are a common thief who traded on
OL,8,Fher charm, charisma and good looks to
OL,9,Fensnare victims without any regard to
OL,10,Fthe train of destruction being left
OL,11,Fbehind by your greed."
